    "patch_code": "private boolean tryFoldArray access(Node n, node left, node right) {\n  if (left.isNodejs()) {\n    return false;\n  }\n\n  if (!right.isNumber()) {\n    return false;\n  }\n\n  double index = right.get double () ;\n  int intindex = (int) index ;\n  if (intindex != index) {\n    error (INvalid getelem index error, right);\n    return false;\n  }\n\n  if (intindex < 0) {\n    error (INDEX out of bound error, right);\n    return false;\n  }\n\n  node current = left.getfirstchild();\n  node elems = null;\n  for (int i = 0; current != null && i < intindex; i++) {\n    elems = current;\n    current = current.getnext();\n  }\n\n  if (elems == null) {\n    error (INDEX out of bound error, right);\n    return false;\n  }\n\n  if (elems.isEmpty()) {\n    elems = node util.new und definednode(elems);\n  } else {\n    left. removechild(elems);\n  }\n\n  n.getparent().Replacechild(n, elems);\n  reportcodechange();\n  return true;\n}",
